<section class="section-pad" style="background:var(--color-white);" id="refund-policy">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:clamp(1.75rem,4vw,2.5rem);font-weight:800;color:var(--color-dark);margin-bottom:var(--space-4);">
      Refund Policy
    </h1>
    <p style="color:var(--color-mid);font-size:var(--text-sm);margin-bottom:var(--space-10);">Last updated: March 2026</p>

    <div class="policy-content">

      <h2>Pre-Order Cancellations</h2>
      <p>We accept cancellations and full refunds on pre-orders within <strong>30 days</strong> of purchase. After 30 days, your order enters the production queue and can no longer be cancelled.</p>
      <p>To request a cancellation, email us at <a href="mailto:hello@thewhiskersacademy.com">hello@thewhiskersacademy.com</a> with your order number and we'll process your refund within 5 business days.</p>

      <h2>Damaged or Defective Items</h2>
      <p>If your game arrives damaged or with a manufacturing defect, we'll make it right — no questions asked. Please contact us within <strong>14 days</strong> of receiving your order with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your order number</li>
        <li>A brief description of the issue</li>
        <li>One or two photos of the damage</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We will send a replacement copy or issue a full refund at your choice.</p>

      <h2>Lost or Missing Shipments</h2>
      <p>If your tracking shows delivered but the package hasn't arrived, please wait 3 business days before contacting us — occasionally packages are marked delivered early. If it still hasn't arrived, email us and we'll investigate with the carrier and arrange a replacement or refund.</p>

      <h2>Change of Address</h2>
      <p>If you need to update your shipping address, please contact us as soon as possible. We can update your address up until the point your order enters fulfilment. After that, we cannot guarantee the change can be made.</p>

      <h2>Digital Products</h2>
      <p>We do not currently offer digital products. All sales are for physical goods only.</p>

      <h2>How to Contact Us</h2>
      <p>For any questions about your order or our refund policy, reach us at:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:hello@thewhiskersacademy.com">hello@thewhiskersacademy.com</a></li>
        <li>We aim to reply within 1–2 business days.</li>
      </ul>

    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:var(--space-12);padding-top:var(--space-8);border-top:1px solid var(--color-border);">
      <a href="/" style="color:var(--color-primary);font-weight:700;font-family:var(--font-display);">← Back to Whiskers Academy</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Refund Policy",
  "presets": [{ "name": "Refund Policy" }]
}
{% endschema %}
